{"tid":561880,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"2018年賀歲片黎講，<<一家大晒>>真係獨佔鰲頭！","createTime":"2018-02-15T11:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T12:32:29.000Z","uid":54025,"like":10,"dislike":143,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f99bb683442f56cf107d4d38e153f31976cf682a","tid":561880,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"如題，睇左&lt;&lt;一家大晒&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;西遊記&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;黑豹&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;棟篤特工&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n我覺得&lt;&lt;一&gt;&gt;真係最高質，全場無冷場，好好笑。個種搞笑好有親切感令人重拾童真。<br />\n<br />\n而低成本制作黎講我比9分(10分滿分) 。 演員選角亦做得好好，李思捷洗盡沿華放低過往既串柒味去飾演一個神經質好爸爸。個種反差真係好令人驚喜。<br />\n驚係因為估佢唔到佢可以轉型得如此成功。<br />\n喜係因為見到佢可以百屌成才而為佢歡喜。<br />\n<br />\n另外配合上其他好戲之人蘇玉華，家英哥，林敏聰，狄龍等等。令成套戲昇華上第2個層次。<br />\n<br />\n劇本都明顯睇得出係大家嘔心瀝血之作。成套戲既搞笑成份我覺得有50%既星爺無厘頭style加50%既本土童真騎呢。<br />\n依種style真係配合得天衣無縫，令人忍俊不禁，笑足全場。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得大家不妨放低對李思捷既偏見，入場睇下依套戲。或者大家會對佢印象改觀。 幾十蚊當支持下本土製作亦未嘗不可<br />\n<br />\n利申：非打手，睇戲多過你柯屎，專業影評人"},{"pid":"27ab80f70b8d1ce831282958ae7aca4b8a2e76ec","tid":561880,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65d496a567b3067094e3e46d2bb87ba185ba8c0","tid":561880,"uid":2333,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:22:27.000Z","msg":"係  好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef47e4b5858953b92b0e91e3f64ce5fe3f3d065","tid":561880,"uid":54025,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係  好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇左一次，諗住初三同屋企人再睇一次<br />\n<br />\n我認為同一家人去睇會係第2種風味<br />\n<br />\n因為套野背後都帶出好多正面訊息。真係發人深省"},{"pid":"ce0f722e6b26ecbaf05ae6f619ded9a77cb0ec62","tid":561880,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be62a240411d45ebbf5c1c5adda728f73442d978","tid":561880,"uid":40470,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾打手<br />\n<br />\n你撕折？<br />\n<br />\n見到就唔想睇<br />\n<br />\n浪費晒套戲其他好既演員"},{"pid":"d8131ad6e8e9c735dd05123ae24f337c7fbb94ce","tid":561880,"uid":92,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:31:20.000Z","msg":"李思捷會唔會係第一個香港人拎奧斯卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2008abed031c21700af6cff5368e3dbac6ba33e6","tid":561880,"uid":40470,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"一齊負評<br />\n<br />\n杜絕打手"},{"pid":"38ccc88efebfa391a5ce60e6a070c92a690c9c06","tid":561880,"uid":27766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"難分真與假"},{"pid":"c563cf2999c893160c0997c9a6871e573924efde","tid":561880,"uid":54025,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:41:13.000Z","msg":"識我既人就知我唔會做打手。<br />\n<br />\n我波台首席kol從來有個句講個句"},{"pid":"4931a343d9bf1c1621362f0556e218ebaffa573e","tid":561880,"uid":117896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:45:41.000Z","msg":"打手正仆街"},{"pid":"ed6f72b0b5ff65e527ec815b8977482827f28d64","tid":561880,"uid":54025,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:47:10.000Z","msg":"點解出面有人吹棟篤特工唔見有人屌佢地係打手?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本就對人不對事先入為主咁睇死李思捷"},{"pid":"ef3b864c31138c14a0510abf1abbe5f4ddccb809","tid":561880,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"諗起佢成日扮聲懶有才華就乞人憎"},{"pid":"a086d267f2407a053551c782c478a4c3590681ad","tid":561880,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":0